{"tid":1372861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再講冷氣軍師，叫大家撤係因為宜家無原因要留，加上防暴人數愈來愈多。","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T15:01:23.000Z","uid":203019,"like":104,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8658ec6cbabf04d7d11c73ae0b10bed109eead21","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆，叫大家走係想大家不流血不被捕，場仗仲有排打，和理非需要勇武派保護，勇武派需要和理非back up同文宣，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n宜家再留係元朗根本無意思。前線手足未必可以時刻留意其他環境即時消息，和理非只係提供更多有用資訊同建議，希望前線手足認真考慮撤退。"},{"pid":"e5434c5a7d151b410c261626b1df571cc395cd6a","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5aaa5a085e49568d37d964f4b413568bf2036167","tid":1372861,"uid":262717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"留力聽日上環"},{"pid":"205f08fb5be17b1c453e27c97c57a4d853814579","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65499aa6745a410c32f42e724041f6235688c4fe","tid":1372861,"uid":231933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6d31b295ad8379a5d23dae02d1f610be1fbc9f","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"356eaf44640f5915e94ee5101e0bbeb4f6fad215","tid":1372861,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點：</span>必須有大家能理解嘅理由。"},{"pid":"b090a6dad722d32d76f3d1483361332d898713d4","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356eaf44640f5915e94ee5101e0bbeb4f6fad215","tid":1372861,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點：</span>必須有大家能理解嘅理由。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09f84ee1de87b63e8957b2f82a76203cceb5dea6","tid":1372861,"uid":288140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"058e2e51fdc436ebdc2ac0a058e9eb1fd8473154","tid":1372861,"uid":222994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:13:53.000Z","msg":"完全唔明呢一刻再留有咩意思"},{"pid":"cd4929ecec525f4e832d4138c13b841eb4a6d33c","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"328aaf89dc0e033ccb5646e2f9e3f8bfe79fde41","tid":1372861,"uid":288140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"愈多勇武被捕，革命成功機會愈細！今次無留低既意義！ 唔好戀戰！ 抗爭既路仲好長"},{"pid":"65b36c319abbf6b652a0f7b400a65259acb3b703","tid":1372861,"uid":79974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>交俾前線決定</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地會比前線接收到更多嘅外界資訊，但同時，前線嘅資訊都係佢地先知，我地只能通知前線，外面發生緊乜<br />\n<br />\n記住，大眾係支援前線，陪伴前線，所以想走嘅，可以自己走，但要成團撤離，自然應該由前線決定，佢地留，我地陪，佢地走，我地走"},{"pid":"5b3267dd2dcbea5583ece01388b7280cd0219856","tid":1372861,"uid":154892,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"講到走好似輸曬咁 咁留係到贏到咩?"},{"pid":"4be864843d7741519de4c5e30133f7f4a2890a96","tid":1372861,"uid":284676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"元朗！真係難攪。。。<br />\n又要防白杉　又要防警犬　！　我知而家講咩都冇用！　但希望手足一定要安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1411a6695cabd9e1b44c34cfe7039ab391114a","tid":1372861,"uid":108687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:16:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong>每一次其實都係學習緊，好多人愈企愈前，每次出嚟嘅準備亦都愈充足</strong></strong>。"},{"pid":"7f8825f45db2eb7fa0c4fffd1459928d664f6e07","tid":1372861,"uid":81663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"1. 呢仗唔係最後一仗<br />\n2. 港鐵唔係老奉車你走，如果元朗冇鐵，入夜喺其他路走，鄉黑就搞鳩你"},{"pid":"fde5a0ef8d0b9bb7ebe524259a110fe43914f5b6","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"大把冷氣軍師都留到七八點，希望前線明白，唔係所有叫人走嘅都無出過去，點都好，不割蓆，只想大家一齊贏"},{"pid":"69e6a2d19368e07c8293bac5b6bdbffe865b0a1c","tid":1372861,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53df38139eaf45f0264f2ea004c50d7d3e35f18d","tid":1372861,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ea3df326c5ca2eedad7700b2223f0f42ef22975","tid":1372861,"uid":50901,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"係喇軍師<br />\n最好全部post 都講呢個話題好唔好？<br />\n你唔理解就講出黎<br />\n唔撚係話無原因要留<br />\n翻去文宣啦屌"},{"pid":"ee2827bffb6e8d0f5f0b608da4daae6c9db9a7b7","tid":1372861,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"唔會割，點撚都唔會割<br />\n最緊要唔好被捕，小心"},{"pid":"87ab738b9a7bbf3af3d02cc423c59d58fa6fb96c","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:20:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a35ce59d9d88bbdc249f3308eab2a1c166af5fbc","tid":1372861,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0648e8eae1cfb97ae71a1902f43905c3346f0162","tid":1372861,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}